{
  "texts": [
    "ChatGPT' s language translation capacity allows learners to input text in their native language and have it automatically translated into their target language (Jiao et al., 2023).",
    "ChatGPT can also generate writing prompts and provide feedback on written work, leading to improvement in learners' writing skills (Baidoo-Anu & Owusu Ansah, 2023).",
    "Although the potential for positive use of ChatGPT in higher education is high, there are concomitant challenges.",
    "One challenge is the concern regarding plagiarism and academic integrity.",
    "AI writing systems are designed to generate text based on a set of parameters or prompts."
  ]
}